	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I have a Good Boy console with a broken AC adapter.
<br />
<br />On the console it says:
<br />Output Voltage: DC 10V
<br />Max Current 850MA
<br />
<br />And on the AC Adapter it says:
<br />Model: AD-0329F
<br />Input: 220V ~ 50Hz
<br />Output: 9V==1A 9VA
<br />
<br />Can I use my NES adapter instead?
<br />
<br />AC Adapter NES-PAL-002
<br />Input: AC220-230V/50Hz
<br />Output: AC 9.8V/1.3A

		

		</td>
	</tr>
