	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can't use NES adapter, it outputs AC, while your clone requires DC. You need a DC adapter. Exact voltage and current is not that important, it can vary a bit - like 850ma-1A, 7V-35V (but don't take it to the extreme, 10-15V is OK).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


