	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Both are fine. However, make sure the polarity is correct. Some DC adapters with the same size of the connector has plus inside, minus outside, others has minus inside, plus outside. There should be a label on the console that shows correct polarity.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

