	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well, if you can disassemble a console, it is very easy to find out the polarity - just check the traces from adapter connector to 7805. One that goes to middle pin is minus, and other that goes to side pin is plus.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


