	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Wait. AC adapter, i.e. AC-AC adapter, does not have polarity - it is Alternating Current at the output. This one is unsuitable for the clone. However, if you adapter is actually AC-DC, i.e. it has Direct Current at the output, it is suitable for the clone, you only need to check the polarity.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


